          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Disks of natural zirconium. Size of samples:",
                "1)for diameter 12 mm, thickness 120micro-m; 2)for",
                "diameter 30 mm, thickness 30 micro-m or 300 micro-m.",
                "Irradiation of samples was done at the 75 mm distance",
                "to T-Ti target at the angles 0, 30, 120, 150 degrees to",
